# Keep the image build context to source only. The relay Dockerfile copies
# Cargo.toml/Cargo.lock + crates/ + src-tauri/; everything below is build
# output, deps, or VCS that the build never needs — excluding it keeps the
# context small (locally it also avoids shipping a multi-GB target/ dir) and
# makes the build independent of a clean checkout.
target
**/target
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
web/build
web/.svelte-kit
*.dmg
*.app
DerivedData
.docs
